#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kcalc; is a calculator for your desktop environment. In the simple mode it "
"can be used for basic arithmetic operations, but provides advanced modes for "
"scientific, statistical and numeral system calculations."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; je kalkulator za vaše namizno okolje. V preprostem načinu se lahko "
"uporablja za osnovne aritmetične operacije, vendar nudi napredne načine za "
"znanstvene, statistične in numerične izračune."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "KCalc"
msgstr "KCalc"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "calculator"
msgstr "kalkulator"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kcalc; offers many more mathematical functions than meets the eye at a "
"first glance. Please study the section on keyboard accelerators and modes in "
"this handbook to learn more about the many functions available."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; ponuja veliko več matematičnih funkcij, kot se zdi na prvi pogled. "
"Preberite razdelek o pospeševalnikih tipkovnice in načinih v tem priročniku, "
"če želite izvedeti več o številnih razpoložljivih funkcijah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to the usual functionality offered by most scientific "
"calculators, &kcalc; offers a number of features, which I think are "
"worthwhile pointing out:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg običajne funkcionalnosti, ki jo ponuja večina znanstvenih "
"kalkulatorjev, &kcalc; ponuja številne funkcije, za katere menim, da jih je "
"vredno poudariti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kcalc; provides trigonometric functions, logic operations, and it is able "
"to do statistical calculations."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; nudi trigonometrične funkcije, logične operacije in je sposoben "
"izvajati statistične izračune."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kcalc; allows you to cut and paste numbers from/into its display."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; vam omogoča, da izrežete in prilepite številke iz/na njegov zaslon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kcalc; features a <firstterm>results-stack</firstterm> which lets you "
"conveniently recall previous results."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; vsebuje <firstterm>sklad rezultatov</firstterm>, ki vam omogoča "
"priročen priklic prejšnjih rezultatov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can configure &kcalc;'s display colors and font."
msgstr "Konfigurirate lahko prikazne barve in pisavo &kcalc;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure &kcalc;'s precision, the number of displayed digits and "
"the number of digits after the period in the settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami lahko konfigurirate natančnost &kcalc;, "
"število prikazanih števk in število števk za piko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kcalc; offers a great number of useful <link linkend=\"key-accels\"> key-"
"bindings</link>, which make using &kcalc; without using a pointing device "
"easy."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; ponuja veliko število uporabnih <link linkend=\"key-accels\"> vezav "
"tipk</link>, ki omogočajo uporabo &kcalc; enostavno brez uporabe kazalne "
"naprave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hint: pressing (and holding) the &Ctrl;-key, displays on every button,the "
"corresponding key-binding."
msgstr ""
"Namig: če pritisnete (in držite) tipko &Ctrl;, se na vsakem gumbu prikaže "
"ustrezna povezava tipk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kcalc; uses <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Calculator_input_methods#Infix_notation\">Infix notation</ulink> which "
"enforces correct order of operations as taught in school; contrary to <ulink "
"url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Calculator_input_methods#Immediate_execution\">Immediate execution</ulink> "
"used by many simple calculators."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; uporablja <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Calculator_input_methods#Infix_notation\">zapis Infiks</ulink>, ki "
"uveljavlja pravilen vrstni red operacij, kot se učijo v šoli; v nasprotju s "
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Calculator_input_methods#Immediate_execution\">Takojšnjo izvedbo</ulink>, ki "
"jo uporabljajo številni preprosti kalkulatorji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Have fun with &kcalc;!"
msgstr "Zabavajte se s &kcalc;!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Bernd.Johannes.Wuebben;"
msgstr "&Bernd.Johannes.Wuebben;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Uporaba"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Usage"
msgstr "Splošna uporaba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"General usage is straightforward and similar to the way most simple "
"scientific calculators operate, but take note of the following special "
"&kcalc; features:"
msgstr ""
"Splošna uporaba je preprosta in podobna načinu delovanja večine preprostih "
"znanstvenih kalkulatorjev, vendar bodite pozorni na naslednje posebne "
"zmožnosti &kcalc;:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Result Stack"
msgstr "Sklad rezultatov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each time you &LMB; click on the <guibutton>=</guibutton> button or press "
"your keyboard's &Enter; or <keysym>=</keysym> keys, the display result is "
"written to &kcalc;'s result stack. You can navigate through the result stack "
"with your keyboard's <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> and <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> keys."
msgstr ""
"Vsakič, ko &LMB; kliknite gumb <guibutton>=</guibutton> ali na tipkovnici "
"pritisnite &Enter; ali <keysym>=</keysym>, se rezultat prikaza zapiše v "
"sklad rezultatov &kcalc;. Po nizu rezultatov se lahko pomikate s tipkama "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> in <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Percent Function"
msgstr "Funkcija odstotkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The percent function works somewhat differently to that on most calculators. "
"However, once understood, its enhanced functionality proves quite useful. "
"See the section about the <link linkend=\"percent\">percent</link> function "
"for further details."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija odstotkov deluje nekoliko drugače kot na večini kalkulatorjev. Ko "
"pa ga razumemo, se njegova izboljšana funkcionalnost izkaže za precej "
"uporabno. Za nadaljnje podrobnosti glejte razdelek o funkciji <link linkend="
"\"percent\">odstotek</link>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cut and Paste"
msgstr "Izreži in prilepi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> will "
"place the displayed number onto the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo>, boste prikazano število postavili na odložišče."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> will "
"paste the clipboard content into the display if the content of the clipboard "
"is a valid floating point number."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo>, boste vsebino odložišča prilepili na zaslon, če je vsebina "
"odložišča veljavno število s plavajočo vejico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is still possible to copy/paste by clicking on &kcalc;'s display, but "
"this may disappear in future versions."
msgstr ""
"Še vedno je mogoče kopirati/prilepiti s klikom na zaslon &kcalc;, vendar bo "
"to v prihodnjih različicah morda izginilo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced functions"
msgstr "Napredne funkcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &kcalc; for the first time, the calculator will only display "
"buttons for basic arithmetic computations."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete &kcalc; kalkulator bo prvič prikazal samo gumbe za osnovne "
"aritmetične izračune."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Under the menu entry <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> it is possible to select a "
"mode for &kcalc;: it is possible to choose <link linkend=\"simple-mode"
"\">Simple</link> or <link linkend=\"science-mode\">Science</link> or <link "
"linkend=\"statistical-mode\">Statistic</link> or <link linkend=\"numeral-"
"system-mode\">Numeral System</link> mode. Please note, that these modes will "
"slightly change as &kcalc; evolves."
msgstr ""
"Pod menijskim vnosom <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> je mogoče izbrati način "
"za &kcalc;: izbrati je mogoče <link linkend=\"simple-mode\">Enostavno</link> "
"ali <link linkend=\"science-mode\">Znanost</link> ali način <link linkend="
"\"statistical-mode\">Statistika</link> ali <link linkend=\"numeral-system-"
"mode\">Številski sistem</link>. Upoštevajte, da se bodo ti načini nekoliko "
"spremenili, ko &kcalc; razvija."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Button Layout"
msgstr "Postavitev gumba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To give easy access to all the functions in advanced modes in &kcalc;, many "
"keys have a second layout. Click on <guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> or press "
"the shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo> "
"to make the second layout of the buttons visible."
msgstr ""
"Za lažji dostop do vseh funkcij v naprednih načinih v &kcalc; ima veliko "
"tipk drugo postavitev. Kliknite <guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> ali "
"pritisnite bližnjico <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>2</keycap></"
"keycombo>, da naredite drugo postavitev gumbov vidno."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "History"
msgstr "Zgodovina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The history area shows all the calculations done in &kcalc; for the active "
"session of &kcalc;. Click on <guibutton>AC</guibutton> or press the shortcut "
"<keycap>Del</keycap> to clear the content of the history. To activate or "
"deactivate it, use the item <guilabel>Show History</guilabel> in the menu "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> of the menu bar, or press <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Območje zgodovine prikazuje vse izračune, opravljene v &kcalc; za aktivno "
"sejo &kcalc;. Kliknite <guibutton>AC</guibutton> ali pritisnite bližnjico "
"<keycap>Del</keycap>, da počistite vsebino zgodovine. Če ga želite "
"aktivirati ali deaktivirati, uporabite element <guilabel>Pokaži zgodovino</"
"guilabel> v meniju <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> v menijski vrstici ali "
"pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H </keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simple Mode"
msgstr "Preprost način"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This mode contains only those buttons and functions, which are essential "
"necessary for basic calculations."
msgstr ""
"Ta način vsebuje samo tiste gumbe in funkcije, ki so nujno potrebni za "
"osnovne izračune."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you just want to sum up all items on an invoice this mode may be your "
"choice."
msgstr ""
"Če želite le sešteti vse postavke na računu, je ta način morda vaša izbira."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "Science Mode"
msgstr "Znanstveni način"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this mode the left column of buttons is allocated to trigonometric "
"functions:"
msgstr ""
"V tem načinu je levi stolpec gumbov dodeljen trigonometričnim funkcijam:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:212 index.docbook:256 index.docbook:317 index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "Buttons"
msgstr "Gumbi"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:213 index.docbook:257 index.docbook:318 index.docbook:376
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid "Function"
msgstr "Funkcija"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:216 index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Hyp</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Hyp</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter Hyperbolic sub mode. Hyp Sin for example is the hyperbolic sine: sinh"
msgstr ""
"Vstopite v podnačin Hyperbolic. Hyp Sin je na primer hiperbolični sinus: sinh"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:220 index.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Sin</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Sin</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the sine"
msgstr "Izračunajte sinus"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift; <guibutton>Sin</guibutton> or <guibutton>Asin</guibutton>"
msgstr "&Shift; <guibutton>Sin</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Asin</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the inverse sine"
msgstr "Izračunajte inverzni sinus"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:226 index.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Cos</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Cos</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the cosine"
msgstr "Izračunajte kosinus"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift; <guibutton>Cos</guibutton> or <guibutton>Acos</guibutton>"
msgstr "&Shift; <guibutton>Cos</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Acos</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the inverse cosine"
msgstr "Izračunajte inverzni kosinus"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:232 index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Tan</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Tan</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the tangent"
msgstr "Izračunaj tangens"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift; <guibutton>Tan</guibutton> or <guibutton>Atan</guibutton>"
msgstr "&Shift; <guibutton>Tan</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Atan</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the inverse tangent"
msgstr "Izračunajte inverzni tangens"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:238 index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Log</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Log</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the Log base 10"
msgstr "Izračunajte osnovo log 10"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift; <guibutton>Log</guibutton> or 10<superscript>x</superscript>"
msgstr "&Shift; <guibutton>Log</guibutton> ali 10<superscript>x</superscript>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute 10 to the power of x"
msgstr "Izračunajte 10 na potenco x"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:244 index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Ln</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Ln</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the natural logarithm. That is the log to base e"
msgstr "Izračunajte naravni logaritem. To je dnevnik do baze e"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift; <guibutton>Ln</guibutton> or e<superscript>x</superscript>"
msgstr "&Shift; <guibutton>Ln</guibutton> ali e<superscript>x</superscript>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute e (the base of the natural logarithm) to the power of x"
msgstr "Izračunajte e (osnovo naravnega logaritma) na potenco x"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "The second column has buttons for algebraic functions:"
msgstr "Drugi stolpec ima gumbe za algebraične funkcije:"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:260 index.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Mod</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Mod</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the remainder in Euclidean division"
msgstr "Izračunajte ostanek pri evklidskem deljenju"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>Mod</guibutton> or "
"<guibutton>IntDiv</guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>Mod</guibutton> ali "
"<guibutton>IntDiv</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Integer division (integer part of the quotient)"
msgstr "Celoštevilsko deljenje (celoštevilski del količnika)"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:266 index.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>1/x</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>1/x</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the reciprocal for a number"
msgstr "Izračunaj recipročno vrednost števila"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>1/x</guibutton> or <guibutton>nCm</"
"guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>1/x</guibutton> ali "
"<guibutton>nCm</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compute the number of distinct second-operand-element subsets of it that can "
"be formed for any set containing first operand elements (binomial "
"coefficient)"
msgstr ""
"Izračunajte število njegovih različnih podmnožic elementov drugega operanda, "
"ki jih je mogoče oblikovati za kateri koli niz, ki vsebuje elemente prvega "
"operanda (binomski koeficient)"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:272 index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>x!</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>x!</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compute the product of all positive integers less than or equal to the "
"current integer operand (factorial)"
msgstr ""
"Izračunaj zmnožek vseh pozitivnih celih števil, manjših ali enakih "
"trenutnemu celemu operandu (faktoriel)"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>x²</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>x²</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the square of x"
msgstr "Izračunaj kvadrat x"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>x²</guibutton> or <guibutton>√x</"
"guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>x²</guibutton> or <guibutton>√x</"
"guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the square root of x"
msgstr "Izračunajte kvadratni koren iz x"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>xʸ</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>xʸ</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "x power y"
msgstr "x potenca y"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&Shift; x<superscript>y</superscript> or x<superscript>1/y</superscript>"
msgstr ""
"&Shift; x<superscript>y</superscript> ali x<superscript>1/y</superscript>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "x power 1/y"
msgstr "x potenca 1/y"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>x³</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>x³</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Computes the third (cubic) power of x"
msgstr "Izračuna tretjo (kubično) potenco x"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>x³</guibutton> or <guibutton>∛x</"
"guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>x³</guibutton> ali <guibutton>∛x</"
"guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid "Computes the third (cubic) root of x"
msgstr "Izračuna tretji (kubični) koren iz x"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "x·10ʸ"
msgstr "x·10ʸ"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Computes the product of the first operand and decimal exponent of the second "
"operand"
msgstr ""
"Izračuna zmnožek prvega operanda in decimalnega eksponenta drugega operanda"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Statistical Mode"
msgstr "Statistični način"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this mode the left column of buttons is allocated to statistical "
"functions:"
msgstr "V tem načinu je levi stolpec gumbov dodeljen statističnim funkcijam:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most of the functionality in this mode is centered around the "
"<guibutton>Dat</guibutton> button. To create a data list of numbers, enter a "
"number into the calculator and press <guibutton>Dat</guibutton>. A "
"sequentially increasing number is shown on the display indicating which "
"position in the Data <quote>list</quote> the number occupies. A traditional "
"calculator only stores three values for statistical functions: The number of "
"discrete items in a list, the sum of the data items entered and the sum of "
"the square of all data items in the list. &kcalc; differs by actually "
"storing each discrete value, allowing you to calculate the median value of "
"the data."
msgstr ""
"Večina funkcionalnosti v tem načinu je osredotočena na gumb <guibutton>Dat</"
"guibutton>. Če želite ustvariti podatkovni seznam številk, vnesite številko "
"v kalkulator in pritisnite <guibutton>Dat</guibutton>. Na zaslonu je "
"prikazano zaporedno naraščajoče število, ki označuje, kateri položaj na "
"<quote>seznamu</quote> podatkov številka zaseda. Tradicionalni kalkulator "
"shrani samo tri vrednosti za statistične funkcije: število diskretnih "
"postavk na seznamu, vsoto vnesenih podatkov in vsoto kvadrata vseh podatkov "
"na seznamu. &kcalc; se razlikuje po dejanskem shranjevanju vsake diskretne "
"vrednosti, kar vam omogoča izračun mediane vrednosti podatkov."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>N</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>N</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recall the number of data items entered"
msgstr "Prikličite število vnesenih podatkovnih elementov"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>N</guibutton> or <guibutton>&Sgr;"
"x</guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>N</guibutton> ali <guibutton>&Sgr;"
"x</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the sum of all data items entered"
msgstr "Prikaži vsoto vseh vnesenih podatkovnih postavk"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Mea</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Mea</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the mean of the data items entered"
msgstr "Prikaži srednjo vrednost vnesenih podatkovnih postavk"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>Mea</guibutton> or <guibutton>&Sgr;"
"x²</guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>Mea</guibutton> ali "
"<guibutton>&Sgr;x²</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the sum of the square of all data items entered"
msgstr "Prikažite vsoto kvadratov vseh vnesenih podatkov"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "&sgr;<subscript>N</subscript>"
msgstr "&sgr;<subscript>N</subscript>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the standard deviation (n)"
msgstr "Prikaži standardni odklon (n)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> &sgr;<subscript>N</subscript> or &sgr;"
"<subscript>N-1</subscript>"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> &sgr;<subscript>N</subscript> ali &sgr;"
"<subscript>N-1</subscript>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the population standard deviation (n-1)"
msgstr "Prikaži standardni odklon populacije (n-1)"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Med</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Med</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the median"
msgstr "Prikažite mediano"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:342 index.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Dat</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Dat</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter a data item"
msgstr "Vnesite podatkovno postavko"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>Dat</guibutton> or "
"<guibutton>CDat</guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>Dat</guibutton> ali "
"<guibutton>CDat</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clear last data item entered"
msgstr "Počisti zadnji vneseni podatek"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>CSt</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>CSt</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clear the store of all data item entered"
msgstr "Počistite shrambo vseh vnesenih podatkovnih elementov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next two columns hold the buttons with trigonometric and algebraic "
"functions described in the <link linkend=\"science-mode\">Science</link> "
"mode section."
msgstr ""
"Naslednja dva stolpca vsebujeta gumbe s trigonometričnimi in algebrskimi "
"funkcijami, opisanimi v razdelku načina <link linkend=\"science-mode"
"\">Znanost</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Numeral System Mode"
msgstr "Način številskega sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This mode contains buttons and functions to calculate in binary, "
"hexadecimal, octal and decimal."
msgstr ""
"Ta način vsebuje gumbe in funkcije za binarno, šestnajstiško, osmiško in "
"decimalno računanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You select the base from the dropdown menu on the left. To insert a "
"hexadecimal number for example, just do the following: Select <guilabel>Hex</"
"guilabel> from the dropdown menu. Then enter a number and note that you can "
"use the letters <guibutton>A</guibutton> to <guibutton>F</guibutton> for "
"digits larger than 9. In the numeral system view, you can see the number "
"converted to decimal, octal and binary."
msgstr ""
"Številski sistem izberete z izbirnimi gumbi na desni. Če želite na primer "
"vstaviti šestnajstiško število, naredite naslednje: Izberite <guilabel>Hex</"
"guilabel> izmed izbirnih gumbov. Nato vnesite število in upoštevajte, da "
"lahko uporabite črke <guibutton>A</guibutton> do <guibutton>F</guibutton> za "
"števke večje od 9. V pogledu številskega sistema lahko vidite število, "
"pretvorjeno v decimalno, osmiško in dvojiško."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Binary, octal and hexadecimal numbers can be displayed as groups of digits "
"separated by whitespaces. Such grouping can improve readability of numbers. "
"For example, hexadecimal number <emphasis>AF1C42</emphasis> can be displayed "
"as <emphasis>AF 1C 42</emphasis> with separation every second digit. "
"Grouping can be turned off or tweaked. Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kcalc;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to "
"bring up the configuration dialog and change the setting on the "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> page as appropriate."
msgstr ""
"Dvojiška, osmiška in šestnajstiška števila so lahko prikazana kot skupine "
"števk ločenih s presledki. Takšno združevanje lahko izboljša berljivost "
"števil. Na primer, šestnajstiško število <emphasis>AF1C42</emphasis> je "
"lahko prikazano kot <emphasis>AF 1C 42</emphasis> z ločitvijo vsake druge "
"števke. Združevanje je mogoče izklopiti ali spremeniti. Izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kcalc;..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da odprete pogovorno okno konfiguracije in "
"spremenite nastavitev na strani <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> kot vam je "
"primerno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may want to select <guimenu>Show Bit Edit</guimenu> from the "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu to see selected bits."
msgstr ""
"Morda boste želeli izbrati <guimenu>Pokaži urejanje bitov</guimenu> v meniju "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu>, da si ogledate izbrane bite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are logic operators available in this mode. These operators are:"
msgstr "V tem načinu so na voljo logični operatorji. Ti operaterji so:"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:378 index.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>AND</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>AND</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid "Two numbers are logically anded"
msgstr "Dve števili sta logično sešteti"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:381 index.docbook:589
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>OR</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>OR</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "Two numbers are logically ored"
msgstr "Dve števili sta logično urejeni"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>XOR</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>XOR</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "Two numbers are logically exclusive ored"
msgstr "Dve številki sta logično izključujoči"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:387 index.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Lsh</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Lsh</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid "Left shift the value"
msgstr "Premik vrednosti v levo"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:390 index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Rsh</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Rsh</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "Right shift the value"
msgstr "Premik vrednosti v desno"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Cmp</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Cmp</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "Perform a 1's complement"
msgstr "Izvedite komplement 1"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The second column holds the buttons with algebraic functions described in "
"the <link linkend=\"science-mode\">Science</link> mode section."
msgstr ""
"Drugi stolpec vsebuje gumbe z algebrskimi funkcijami, opisanimi v razdelku "
"<link linkend=\"science-mode\">Znanost</link> načina."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The third column with the buttons <guibutton>A</guibutton> to <guibutton>F</"
"guibutton> is enabled only in <guilabel>Hex</guilabel> mode."
msgstr ""
"Tretji stolpec z gumbi <guibutton>A</guibutton> do <guibutton>F</guibutton> "
"je omogočen samo v <guilabel>Šestnajstiškem</guilabel> načinu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid "Memory Operations"
msgstr "Pomnilniške operacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kcalc; supports the memory operations given by standard calculators plus "
"six slots to hold constants."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; podpira pomnilniške operacije, ki jih ponujajo standardni "
"kalkulatorji, plus šest rež za shranjevanje konstant."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Standard Memory Operations"
msgstr "Standardne pomnilniške operacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kcalc; can remember results of operations for you, and re-use them in later "
"calculations. You can access these functions via several buttons labeled "
"<guibutton>MR</guibutton>, <guibutton>MS</guibutton>, <guibutton>M+</"
"guibutton> and <guibutton>MC</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; lahko namesto vas zapomni rezultate operacij in jih ponovno uporabi "
"v kasnejših izračunih. Do teh funkcij lahko dostopate prek več gumbov z "
"oznakami <guibutton>MR</guibutton>, <guibutton>MS</guibutton>, <guibutton>M"
"+</guibutton> in <guibutton>MC</guibutton>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>MS</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>MS</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>MS</guibutton> button stores the currently displayed result "
"in memory."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>MS</guibutton> shrani trenutno prikazan rezultat v pomnilnik."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>M+</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>M+</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>M+</guibutton> button adds the current result to the one in "
"memory. So, if you had stored a 20, and the current result is a 5, your "
"memory would contain 25 when you press it. If the memory is empty, it acts "
"like <guibutton>MS</guibutton> and simply stores the result."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>M+</guibutton> doda trenutni rezultat tistemu v pomnilniku. "
"Torej, če ste shranili 20 in je trenutni rezultat 5, bi vaš spomin vseboval "
"25, ko ga pritisnete. Če je pomnilnik prazen, deluje kot <guibutton>MS</"
"guibutton> in preprosto shrani rezultat."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>MR</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>MR</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>MR</guibutton> button gets the value stored in memory and "
"puts it in the display."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>MR</guibutton> pridobi vrednost, shranjeno v pomnilniku, in "
"jo prikaže na zaslonu."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>MC</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>MC</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guibutton>MC</guibutton> button clears the memory."
msgstr "Gumb <guibutton>MC</guibutton> poÄisti pomnilnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a value is stored in memory a <guilabel>M</guilabel> will appear in the "
"status bar, next to the calculator mode indicator"
msgstr ""
"Če je vrednost shranjena v pomnilniku, se v statusni vrstici poleg "
"indikatorja načina kalkulatorja prikaže <guilabel>M</guilabel>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constants"
msgstr "Konstante"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The six constants buttons <guibutton>C1</guibutton> to <guibutton>C6</"
"guibutton> will only be visible after activating the item "
"<guilabel>Constants Buttons</guilabel> in the menu <guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> of the menu bar. They are available in <guilabel>Science mode</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Statistics mode</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Šest gumbov za konstante <guibutton>C1</guibutton> do <guibutton>C6</"
"guibutton> bo vidnih šele po aktiviranju elementa <guilabel>Gumbi za "
"konstante</guilabel> v meniju <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> menijske "
"vrstice. Na voljo so v <guilabel>znanstvenem načinu</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>statističnem načinu</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see the value stored in each constant hover the button with the mouse "
"pointer."
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati vrednost, shranjeno v vsaki konstanti, z miškinim "
"kazalcem premaknite gumb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To store the number shown in the &kcalc; display in one of the six "
"constants, first press <guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> followed by the "
"desired button key <guibutton>C1</guibutton> up to <guibutton>C6</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Za shranjevanje številke, prikazane v &kcalc; prikaz v eni od šestih "
"konstant, najprej pritisnite <guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton>, nato pa želeno "
"tipko gumba <guibutton>C1</guibutton> do <guibutton>C6</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use the value stored in any of the constants in a calculation, just press "
"the desired button (<guibutton>C1</guibutton> to <guibutton>C6</guibutton>), "
"and the corresponding number will appear in the display."
msgstr ""
"Če želite v izračunu uporabiti vrednost, shranjeno v kateri koli konstanti, "
"preprosto pritisnite želeni gumb (<guibutton>C1</guibutton> do "
"<guibutton>C6</guibutton>) in ustrezna številka se prikaže na zaslonu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to change the label of the constants button to make it easier "
"to remember which button holds which constant. Click with the right mouse "
"button on one of the buttons <guibutton>C1</guibutton> to <guibutton> C6</"
"guibutton>. A popup menu appears, in which you select <guilabel> Set Name</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Možno je spremeniti oznako gumba za konstante, da si lažje zapomnimo, kateri "
"gumb ima katero konstanto. Z desnim gumbom miške kliknite enega od gumbov "
"<guibutton>C1</guibutton> do <guibutton> C6</guibutton>. Prikaže se pojavni "
"meni, v katerem izberete <guilabel> Nastavi ime</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are many (mostly physical) predefined constants, which can be put on "
"any of the six buttons <guibutton>C1</guibutton> - <guibutton>C6</guibutton> "
"by selecting the desired constant in the popup menu that appears after right "
"clicking on one of the constant buttons and selecting <guilabel>Choose from "
"List</guilabel>. Though the predefined constants can also be accessed via "
"the <guimenu>Constants</guimenu> in the menu bar, storing it on a constants "
"button is very handy, if the number is used frequently."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja veliko (večinoma fizičnih) vnaprej določenih konstant, ki jih lahko "
"postavite na katerega koli od šestih gumbov <guibutton>C1</guibutton> - "
"<guibutton>C6</guibutton> tako, da izberete želeno konstanto v pojavnem "
"meniju, ki se prikaže za desno. s klikom na enega od stalnih gumbov in "
"izbiro <guilabel>Izberi s seznama</guilabel>. Čeprav lahko do vnaprej "
"določenih konstant dostopate tudi prek <guimenu>Konstante</guimenu> v "
"menijski vrstici, je shranjevanje na gumb za konstante zelo priročno, če "
"število pogosto uporabljate."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Single Key Accelerators"
msgstr "Pospeševalniki z enim ključem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To simplify entering calculations from the keyboard &kcalc; has single key "
"accelerators for most functions. For example entering <userinput>7R</"
"userinput> or <userinput>7r</userinput> will calculate the reciprocal of 7 "
"(1/7)."
msgstr ""
"Za poenostavitev vnašanja izračunov s tipkovnico &kcalc; ima pospeševalnike "
"z eno tipko za večino funkcij. Če na primer vnesete <userinput>7R</"
"userinput> ali <userinput>7r</userinput>, boste izračunali recipročno "
"vrednost 7 (1/7)."

