#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mod and IntDiv"
msgstr "Mod in IntDiv"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Mod</guibutton> gives the remainder of dividing the displayed "
"number by the next input number."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Mod</guibutton> poda preostanek deljenja prikazanega števila z "
"naslednjim vnesenim številom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>22 Mod 8 = </userinput> will give the result <emphasis>6</"
"emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>22 Mod 8 = </userinput> bo dal rezultat <emphasis>6</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>22.345 Mod 8 = </userinput> will give the result <emphasis>6.345</"
"emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>22.345 Mod 8 = </userinput> bo dal rezultat <emphasis>6.345</"
"emphasis>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>IntDiv</guibutton> does integer "
"division of the displayed number by the next input number."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>IntDiv</guibutton> celoštevilsko "
"deli prikazano število z naslednjim vnesenim številom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>22 Shift IntDiv 8 = </userinput> will give the result "
"<emphasis>2</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>22 Shift IntDiv 8 = </userinput> bo dal rezultat <emphasis>2</"
"emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>22.345 Shift IntDiv 8 = </userinput> also gives <emphasis>2</"
"emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>22.345 Shift IntDiv 8 = </userinput> daje tudi <emphasis>2</"
"emphasis>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:675
#, no-c-format
msgid "&percnt;"
msgstr "&percnt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Used instead of the <guibutton>=</guibutton> key, <guibutton>%</guibutton> "
"interprets the final operation carried out in the current calculation as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabljen namesto tipke <guibutton>=</guibutton>, <guibutton>%</guibutton> "
"interpretira končno operacijo, izvedeno v trenutnem izračunu, kot sledi:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the final operator is + or - the second argument is interpreted as "
"percentage of the first operand."
msgstr ""
"Če je končni operator + ali -, se drugi argument interpretira kot odstotek "
"prvega operanda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the final operator is * divide the result of the multiplication by 100."
msgstr "Če je končni operator *, rezultat množenja delite s 100."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the final operator is / give the left operand as a percentage of the "
"right operand."
msgstr ""
"Če je končni operator /, podajte levi operand kot odstotek desnega operanda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:696
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In all other cases the &percnt; key gives identical results to the = key."
msgstr ""
"V vseh drugih primerih je &percnt; tipka daje enake rezultate kot tipka =."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples:"
msgstr "Primeri:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>150 + 50 %</userinput> gives <emphasis>225</emphasis> (150 plus "
"50 percent of this amount)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>150 + 50 %</userinput> da <emphasis>225</emphasis> (150 plus 50 "
"odstotkov tega zneska)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>42 * 3 %</userinput> gives <emphasis>1.26</emphasis> (42 * 3 / "
"100)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>42 * 3 %</userinput> daje <emphasis>1,26</emphasis> (42 * 3 / 100)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>45 / 55 %</userinput> gives <emphasis>81.81...</emphasis> (45 is "
"81.81.. percent of 55)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>45 / 55 %</userinput> daje <emphasis>81,81...</emphasis> (45 je "
"81,81.. odstotkov od 55)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:717
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lsh and Rsh"
msgstr "Lsh in Rsh"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Lsh</guibutton> left shifts the integer part of the displayed "
"value (multiplies it by 2) n times, where n is the next input number, and "
"gives an integer result (base is set to <guibutton>Bin</guibutton>):"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Lsh</guibutton> premakne celoštevilski del prikazane vrednosti n-"
"krat (pomnoži ga z 2), kjer je n naslednja vnesena številka, in da "
"celoštevilski rezultat (osnova je nastavljena na <guibutton>Bin</guibutton>):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>10 Lsh 3 =</userinput> gives <emphasis>80</emphasis> (10 "
"multiplied by 2 three times)."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>10 Lsh 3 =</userinput> daje <emphasis>80</emphasis> (10 pomnoženo "
"z 2 trikrat)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:725
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>10.345 Lsh 3 =</userinput> also gives <emphasis>80</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>10,345 Lsh 3 =</userinput> daje tudi <emphasis>80</emphasis>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Rsh</guibutton> right shifts the value (performs an integer "
"divide by 2) n times."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Rsh</guibutton> desno premakne vrednost (izvede deljenje celega "
"števila z 2) n-krat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>16 Rsh 2 =</userinput> gives <emphasis>4</emphasis> (16 divided "
"by 2 twice)."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>16 Rsh 2 =</userinput> daje <emphasis>4</emphasis> (16 deljeno z "
"2 dvakrat)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>16.999 Rsh 2 =</userinput> also gives <emphasis>4</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>16,999 Rsh 2 =</userinput> daje tudi <emphasis>4</emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cmp, And, Or and Xor"
msgstr "Cmp, And, Or in Xor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Cmp</guibutton>, <guibutton>And</guibutton> and "
"<guibutton>Or</guibutton> functions perform bitwise logical operations and "
"therefore appear more meaningful if the base is set to <guilabel>Hex</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Oct</guilabel> or <guilabel>Bin</guilabel> rather than "
"<guilabel>Dec</guilabel>. In the following examples base is set to "
"<guilabel>Bin</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Funkcije <guibutton>Cmp</guibutton>, <guibutton>And</guibutton> in "
"<guibutton>Or</guibutton> izvajajo bitne logične operacije in so zato videti "
"bolj smiselne, če je osnova nastavljena na <guilabel>Hex</guilabel >, "
"<guilabel>Oct</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Bin</guilabel> namesto <guilabel>dec</"
"guilabel>. V naslednjih primerih je osnova nastavljena na <guilabel>Bin</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:754
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Cmp</guibutton> performs a 1's complement (inverts the bits)."
msgstr "<guibutton>Cmp</guibutton> izvaja komplement 1 (obrne bite)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>101 Cmp</userinput> gives <emphasis>111...111010</emphasis>"
msgstr "<userinput>101 Cmp</userinput> daje <emphasis>111...111010</emphasis>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:761
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>AND</guibutton> does a logical AND."
msgstr "<guibutton>IN</guibutton> naredi logični IN."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>101 AND 110 =</userinput> gives <emphasis>100</emphasis>"
msgstr "<userinput>101 IN 110 =</userinput> daje <emphasis>100</emphasis>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:767
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>OR</guibutton> does the logical OR."
msgstr "<guibutton>ALI</guibutton> naredi logični ALI."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>101 OR 110 =</userinput> gives <emphasis>111</emphasis>"
msgstr "<userinput>101 ALI 110 =</userinput> daje <emphasis>111</emphasis>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>XOR</guibutton> performs the logical XOR (exclusive OR) operation."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>XOR</guibutton> izvede logično operacijo XOR (izključni ALI)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:775
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>101 XOR 110 =</userinput> gives <emphasis>11</emphasis>"
msgstr "<userinput>101 XOR 110 =</userinput> daje <emphasis>11</emphasis>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:785
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "Vprašanja in odgovori"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I get e, the Euler number?"
msgstr "Kako dobim e, Eulerjevo število?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:792
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <userinput>1 Shift e<superscript>x</superscript></userinput> in the "
"&kcalc; window, press <userinput>1 <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo> <keycap>N</keycap></userinput> on the keyboard "
"or use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Constants</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mathematics</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <userinput>1 Shift e<superscript>x</superscript></userinput> v "
"oknu &kcalc; pritisnite <userinput>1 <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo> <keycap>N</keycap></userinput> na tipkovnici "
"ali uporabite <menuchoice> Meni <guimenu>Konstante</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Matematika</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:799
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I get two fixed digits after the period?"
msgstr "Kako dobim dve fiksni števki po piki?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:800
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem> Configure "
"&kcalc;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> on the menu bar, this will bring up "
"the configuration dialog. Check <guilabel>Set decimal precision</guilabel> "
"and adjust the spin control so that it shows a 2."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem> Konfiguriraj "
"&kcalc;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v orodni vrstici, s tem se prikaže  "
"pogovorno okno konfiguracije. Označite <guilabel>Nastavi decimalno "
"natančnost</guilabel> in prilagodite vrtenje tako, da prikazuje 2."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:807
#, no-c-format
msgid "What about Precision?"
msgstr "Kaj pa Natančnost?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main factor determining the precision of &kcalc; is whether your libc "
"and libmath supports the C data type <type>long double</type>. If this is "
"the case, &kcalc; will detect this at compile time and use it as its "
"fundamental data type to represent numbers."
msgstr ""
"Glavni dejavnik, ki določa natančnost &kcalc; ali vaša libc in libmath "
"podpirata podatkovni tip C <type>long double</type>. Če je temu tako, "
"&kcalc; bo to zaznal v času prevajanja in uporabil kot temeljni podatkovni "
"tip za predstavitev števil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:813
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adjust the <guilabel>Precision</guilabel> in &kcalc;'s <guibutton>Configure</"
"guibutton> dialog so that the above computations work correctly. I recommend "
"a precision of 14 if the fundamental data type for your copy of &kcalc; is "
"<type>long double</type>, otherwise 8 or 10."
msgstr ""
"Prilagodite <guilabel>Natančnost</guilabel> v pogovornem oknu &kcalc; "
"<guibutton>Konfiguracija</guibutton>, tako da bodo zgornji izračuni delovali "
"pravilno. Priporočam natančnost 14, če osnovni podatkovni tip za vašo kopijo "
"&kcalc; je <type>long double</type>, sicer 8 ali 10."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Higher precision doesn't necessarily lead to better results. Play with the "
"precision and you will see what I mean."
msgstr ""
"Večja natančnost ne vodi nujno do boljših rezultatov. Igrajte z natančnostjo "
"in videli boste, kaj mislim."

